@page "/AboutCompany/"

<!-- Include the CSS file -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/AboutCompany.css" />

<style>
    /* Header styling */
    header {
        background-color: #013220;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    /* Section styling */
    section {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    /* Title styling */
    h1 {
        color: #013220;
        font-family: 'Palatino', 'URW Palladio L', serif;
    }

    /* Paragraph styling with Georgia font */
    p {
        color: #333;
        font-family: 'Palatino', 'URW Palladio L', serif;
    }

    /* Additional paragraph styling with Georgia font */
    .additional-info {
        font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
    }

    /* List styling */
    ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

    li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Link styling */
    a {
        color: #007BFF;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

</style>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Company</title>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Company</h1>
    </header>

    <section>
        <div class="milestone">
            <h2>Our Milestone</h2>
            <p>
                VitalMed Solutions is a healthcare monitoring website developed by a private clinic under the same company to provide an integrated platform for patients, doctors, and administrative staff.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="overview">
            <h2>Our Overview</h2>
            <p>
                This user-friendly system will be used to manage appointments, access medical records, and monitor patient health metrics in real-time. As our targeted audience is skewed towards the older aged group, our system will have to be easy and simple to use.
            </p>
            <p class="quote">"Bringing healthcare to your fingertips with simplicity and ease."</p>
        </div>

        <div class="goals">
            <h2>Our Goals</h2>
            <p>
                Some aunties and uncles may find it troublesome and inconvenient to check in their health every day, some may also forget the doctor's instructions such as taking pills or exercising. Additionally, it may be harder for them to keep up with the advancement in technology. Thus, our website will help provide this ease of convenience, as well as aid the doctors in ensuring that patients are doing their best to recover.
            </p>
        </div>

        <p>
            For more information, feel free to <a href="ContactUs">contact us</a>.
        </p>
    </section>
</body>
